data.description:
要修改的字段内容，格式：{"_widget_xxx":{"value":值}}。子表单行需含_id字段以保留原行。各字段类型的value格式：
- text/textarea: 字符串，如 {"value":"文本"}
- number: 数字，如 {"value":100}
- datetime: ISO字符串，如 {"value":"2026-01-01T10:00:00.000Z"}
- radiogroup/combo(单选): 字符串，如 {"value":"选项一"}
- checkboxgroup/combocheck(多选): 数组，如 {"value":["选项一","选项二"]}
- phone(电话): 对象，如 {"value":{"phone":"13800138000"}}
- address(地址): 对象，如 {"value":{"province":"省","city":"市","district":"区","detail":"详细地址"}}
- location(定位): 对象含lnglatXY，如 {"value":{"province":"省","city":"市","district":"区","detail":"地址","lnglatXY":[经度,纬度]}}
- user(成员单选): username字符串，如 {"value":"username"}
- usergroup(成员多选): username数组，如 {"value":["user1","user2"]}
- dept(部门单选): dept_no数字，如 {"value":12}
- deptgroup(部门多选): dept_no数组，如 {"value":[12,13]}
- image/upload(图片/附件): 文件key数组，如 {"value":["file-key-1","file-key-2"]}
- subform(子表单): 数组，每行含子字段，如 {"value":[{"_widget_child":{"value":"值"}}]}
